<dashboard version="1.1" hideEdit="true" hideFilters="true">
  <label>tbti 命令帮助</label>

  <row>
    <panel>
      <html>
        <h2>tbti — ThreatBook TI 威胁情报富化命令</h2>
        <p>对 Splunk 事件字段调用 ThreatBook API 进行威胁情报富化，结果自动缓存到 KVStore。</p>

        <h3>语法</h3>
        <pre>... | tbti api=&lt;api_name&gt; [ip=&lt;field&gt;] [ioc=&lt;field&gt;] [url=&lt;field&gt;] [hash=&lt;field&gt;] [nocache=true|false]</pre>

        <h3>参数说明</h3>
        <table style="width:100%; border-collapse:collapse;">
          <tr style="background:#1a1a2e; color:#fff;">
            <th style="padding:8px; text-align:left; border:1px solid #444;">参数</th>
            <th style="padding:8px; text-align:left; border:1px solid #444;">必填</th>
            <th style="padding:8px; text-align:left; border:1px solid #444;">说明</th>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;"><code>api</code></td>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;">是</td>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;">接口类型：<code>ip_reputation</code> | <code>compromise</code> | <code>file_multiengine</code> | <code>url_reputation</code></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background:#f9f9f9;">
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;"><code>ip</code></td>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;">条件必填</td>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;">IP 字段名（配合 <code>api=ip_reputation</code> 使用）</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;"><code>ioc</code></td>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;">条件必填</td>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;">IOC 字段名，支持 IP 或域名（配合 <code>api=compromise</code> 使用）</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background:#f9f9f9;">
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;"><code>url</code></td>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;">条件必填</td>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;">URL 字段名（配合 <code>api=url_reputation</code> 使用）</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;"><code>hash</code></td>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;">条件必填</td>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;">文件哈希字段名，支持 MD5/SHA256（配合 <code>api=file_multiengine</code> 使用）</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background:#f9f9f9;">
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;"><code>nocache</code></td>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;">否</td>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;">默认 <code>false</code>。设为 <code>true</code> 跳过缓存读取，强制调用 API（结果仍写入缓存）</td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <h3>输出字段</h3>
        <table style="width:100%; border-collapse:collapse;">
          <tr style="background:#1a1a2e; color:#fff;">
            <th style="padding:8px; text-align:left; border:1px solid #444;">API</th>
            <th style="padding:8px; text-align:left; border:1px solid #444;">输出字段</th>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;">ip_reputation</td>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;"><code>tb_is_malicious</code> <code>tb_confidence_level</code> <code>tb_severity</code> <code>tb_judgments</code> <code>tb_tags_classes</code> <code>tb_country</code> <code>tb_country_code</code> <code>tb_province</code> <code>tb_city</code></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background:#f9f9f9;">
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;">compromise</td>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;"><code>tb_is_malicious</code> <code>tb_confidence_level</code> <code>tb_severity</code> <code>tb_judgments</code> <code>tb_tags_classes</code></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;">file_multiengine</td>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;"><code>tb_threat_level</code> <code>tb_is_white</code> <code>tb_detected_engines</code> <code>tb_scanned_engines</code> <code>tb_positives</code> <code>tb_scan_date</code> <code>tb_malware_type</code> <code>tb_malware_family</code></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background:#f9f9f9;">
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;">url_reputation</td>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;"><code>tb_threat_level</code> <code>tb_positives</code> <code>tb_ratio</code> <code>tb_sandbox_threat_level</code> <code>tb_sandbox_submit_time</code> <code>tb_sandbox_file_name</code> <code>tb_sandbox_sample_sha256</code> <code>tb_sandbox_type_list</code></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;">通用（所有 API）</td>
            <td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #444;"><code>_key</code> <code>_entity</code> <code>_cached_at</code> <code>_expire_at</code> <code>_ttl_seconds</code> <code>_api_region</code> <code>_cache_policy</code></td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <h3>使用示例</h3>

        <p><strong>IP 信誉查询</strong></p>
        <pre>index=firewall | tbti api=ip_reputation ip=src_ip | table src_ip tb_is_malicious tb_severity tb_judgments</pre>

        <p><strong>只看恶意 IP</strong></p>
        <pre>index=firewall | tbti api=ip_reputation ip=src_ip | where tb_is_malicious="1" | table src_ip tb_severity tb_confidence_level tb_judgments</pre>

        <p><strong>文件多引擎检测</strong></p>
        <pre>index=endpoint | tbti api=file_multiengine hash=file_hash | table file_hash tb_threat_level tb_detected_engines tb_malware_type tb_malware_family</pre>

        <p><strong>URL 信誉查询</strong></p>
        <pre>index=proxy | tbti api=url_reputation url=request_url | table request_url tb_threat_level tb_positives tb_ratio</pre>

        <p><strong>IOC 失陷检测（域名/IP 混合）</strong></p>
        <pre>index=dns | tbti api=compromise ioc=query | table query tb_is_malicious tb_severity tb_judgments</pre>

        <p><strong>强制刷新缓存</strong></p>
        <pre>index=firewall | tbti api=ip_reputation ip=src_ip nocache=true | table src_ip tb_is_malicious tb_severity</pre>

        <p><strong>去重后批量富化（推荐大数据量场景）</strong></p>
        <pre>index=firewall | dedup src_ip | tbti api=ip_reputation ip=src_ip | table src_ip tb_is_malicious tb_severity tb_judgments</pre>

        <p><strong>judgment 标签统计</strong></p>
        <pre>index=firewall | tbti api=ip_reputation ip=src_ip | where tb_is_malicious="1" | mvexpand tb_judgments | stats count by tb_judgments | sort -count</pre>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>
</dashboard>
